### Pipeline Architecture

```
Input → [Pass 1: Summarize] → [Pass 2: Expand + Drift 5%]
      → [Pass 3: Diversify] → [Pass 4: Polish + Drift 8%]
      → Candidate
      ×6 style profiles (multi-style sampling)
      → Critic selects best → Output
```

For long documents (>500 tokens): semantic chunking → per-chunk rewrite with cross-chunk context (60 tokens) → coherence stitching.

### Updated API
- `/api/v1/rewrite` now uses the full multi-pass pipeline
- Supports `style_profile`, [style_vector](file:///D:/Projects/Humanizer/humanizer/style/prefix_encoder.py#56-72), and `pipeline_mode` parameters
- Auto-detects long-form text and switches to document pipeline

